    For the circuit in Figure 7:

    <\padded-center>
      <image|<tuple|<#>|png>|0.6par|0.35par||>

      Figure 7
    </padded-center>

    The switch is closed at <math|t=0>,<math|V<rsub|c><around*|(|0<rsup|->|)>=3 V, i<rsub|L><around*|(|0<rsup|->|)>=-1 A>. Find <math|V<rsub|c><around*|(|t|)>> for <math|t\<gtr\>0>.
